<idea-plugin>
    <id>com.ontalent.ftcsnippets</id>
    <name>FTC Snippets</name>
    <vendor>LTC7 Programming team (#23594)</vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[
<p><b>NOTE: This only works with the FTC SDK. You must download that before using this plugin, otherwise it's pointless. </b> </p>
<p>FTC Snippets adds one-click code templates and import snippets for <b>FIRST Tech Challenge (FTC)</b> robot development.</p>

<p>Features:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Automatically inserts the required <code>package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode;</code> line</li>
    <li>Adds imports for motors, servos, sensors, IMU, and vision</li>
    <li>Optional injection of TeleOp and Autonomous skeleton code</li>
</ul>

<p>Boost your productivity and get your robot code running faster!</p>

<p>Fill out the form for plugin improvements:
<a href="https://forms.gle/wPVPQSpShxgDJXgD6">Google Form</a></p>

]]></description>

    <change-notes><![CDATA[
<p><b>Version 1.0.1 - First Update</b></p>

<p>This update adds small but handy enhancements to FTC Snippets:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Added the ability to automatically insert HardwareMap variables into your code.</li>
    <li>When generating TeleOp or Autonomous skeletons, the class name now automatically matches the file/class name to reduce typos.</li>
</ul>

<p>Access these features via the editor right-click menu or the main toolbar. Happy coding!</p>
]]></change-notes>

